{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta gahje wiꞥſch ar teem:\nRad tee nu pee Jardana nahze/\ntad nozirte tee Kohlus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikkahs/kad weens\nkahou Balki zirte/ tad kritte ta\nZirwja Dſelse uhdeni/ tad fahze\ntas brehkt / un fazzija : Waj\nmans Kungś! ir tas pats irr\naisnemts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Deewa Wihrs fazz-\nzija: Kur tas eekritte? tad rah-\ndija tas winnam to Weetu / un\nwiꞥſch nogreese weenn Kohkn /\nun eegrühde tur patt/tad pelde-\nja ta Dſelse.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Pazell\nto. Tad issteepe tas jawu Roh-\nfu/ un nehme to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Sihreu Kehniſch\ncarroja prett Israëlu/ un aprun-\nnajahs ar fatweem Kalpeem / un\nfazzija: Mehs apmettiſimeeß tai\nun tai Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas Deewa Wihrs\nfuhttja us to Israëta Kehniu/\nun fazzija: Gargajs/ ka tu zaur\nfcho Weetu ne eij/ jo tee Sihrei\nirr tur nonahkaschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhttja tas Israëta\nKehniſch us to Weetu/no ka tas\nDeewa Wihrs tam bij fazzijß/\nun fargaja to/ un paſargajahs\ntur pats/ to darrija wiꞥſch wai-\nrah ne ka weenn un ohtru Lahgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tappe ta Sihreu\nKehnina Sirgś ſeunmiga pahr\nfcho Leetu / un wiꞥſch aizinaja\nfawns Kalpuß / un fazzija us\nteem: Ar juhs man ne grib-\nbat ſtahſicht / kurſch no muhſu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija weens no\nwinna Kalpeem : Ne / mans\nKungś Kehniſch/ tas Praaweets\nEllsus/ kas Israëta Starpâ irr/\nstahsta tam Israëta Kehnimam\ntohś Wahrdus/ ko tu tawa Kam-\nbari runna/ kur tawa Gustatr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Eita/\nun raugajt / kur tas irr/ ka es\nfuhtu un winnu atweddu. Tad\ntappe winnam fluddinahts un\nfazzihts : Rangi / wiꞥſch irr\nDotana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuhttja wiꞥſch us\nturren Sirgue un Rattus / un\nweenu leelu Karra-Spehku / un\ntee nahze Nakti/ un mettehs ap-\nkahrt to Pilsfahtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta Deewa Wihra Sul-\nlainis zehlehs agri/ un igahje /\nun rangi/ weens Karra-Spehks\nbij apkahrt to Pilsfahtu mettees\nar Sirgeem un Ratteem. Tad\nmans Kungś! ko mehs darrifim?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Ne\nbihstees/ jo wairak irr to/ kas pee\nmuins irr / ne ka to / kas pee\nwinneem irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Elisus peeluhdse / un\nfazzija: KUNGŚ/ atdarri jelle\nwinnam tahś Azzis/ ka tas reds:\nTad atdarrija tas KUNGŚ ta\nPuitcha Azzis/ ka tas redseja/\nun rangi/ tas Kalns bija pilns\nuggunigu Sirgu un Rattu ap-\nkahrt Elisu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad tee nu pee ta nonahze/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
